import React from "react"; import { Row, Col, Container } from "reactstrap"; export default class extends React.Component { render() { const { selectInfo } = this.props; const { flight_data } = selectInfo; let info_flight = !flight_data ? '-' : flight_data ? flight_data[0] : [] return (
{info_flight && info_flight.flight_info && info_flight.flight_info.detail.length && info_flight.flight_info.detail.map((item, i) => { return (
Airlines : {item === null ? '-' : item.airlines_name} Flight Number : {item === null ? '-' : item.flight_number} Service Class : {item === null ? '-' : item.service_class} Departure Airport Name : {item === null ? '-' : item.departure_airport_name} City Name : {item === null ? '-' : item.departure_city_name} Time : {item === null ? '-' : item.simple_departure_time} Date : {item === null ? '-' : item.string_departure_date} Arrival Airport Name : {item === null ? '-' : item.arrival_airport_name} City Name : {item === null ? '-' : item.arrival_city_name} Time : {item === null ? '-' : item.simple_arrival_time} Date : {item === null ? '-' : item.string_arrival_date}
) }) }
); } }
